{"id": "1186588452364505159", "channel_id": "1186588452364505159", "type": 0, "author_id": "645085941882552341", "author_name": "initialnote", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2023-12-19T08:38:52.791000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1186588452817485874", "filename": "Screenshot_20231219_163159.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 157439, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186588452364505159/1186588452817485874/Screenshot_20231219_163159.jpg?ex=6a00441c&is=69fef29c&hm=4333f78fad0293459418a070875bcef8524541436cc80517047c2cb6a7dbc212&"}, {"id": "1186588453148827768", "filename": "Screenshot_20231219_163153.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 88117, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186588452364505159/1186588453148827768/Screenshot_20231219_163153.jpg?ex=6a00441c&is=69fef29c&hm=5f5b6187a18ad604bccee3e97d9c4887e3e3c0710fe17d3180c0684d328a41ff&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1186588452364505159", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」請問隕日描寫的增加14%爆擊率實際上有作用嗎？因為不論是戰鬥中查看或是腳色詳細似乎都沒有寫上去", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1186705547957899356", "channel_id": "1186705547957899356", "type": 0, "author_id": "304579470596112385", "author_name": "huseven", "author_bot": false, "content": "我個人覺得\"密契\"再遊戲裡跟命輪一樣都算是讓腳色隊伍質變的因素，但是商店有很多用特殊資源去做更換的密契箱，若用深潛或是相位去做兌換也還能接受畢竟是農素材，但用沉澱去做更換我個人覺得有點下不了手，(畢竟原型視界跟循環母版更香、投資比較有保障腳色技能命輪素質不用去賭但密契箱每個套件要賭)，沉澱是用喚醒獲得的資源非常寶貴，相信這個想法的玩家不只我一個吧?獲取難的狀況下，在好用的密契，也是只有少少的人使用的起，受限資源變相的就還是來來去去那幾套，身為一個Rogue的遊戲變化性少就相對在本質上扣了分，希望官方可以再考慮看看這部分能不能改?感謝!\n\nP.S.直白地說發文者想爽又不想花大錢(?", "timestamp": "2023-12-19T16:24:10.556000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1186705548385726545", "filename": "Screenshot_20231219_235150.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 98736, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186705547957899356/1186705548385726545/Screenshot_20231219_235150.jpg?ex=6a00b12a&is=69ff5faa&hm=baca0b8c409a609de25e67fd04d8d721f29c1720d11e0b07895a9a25abf015d1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1186705547957899356", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」小小的想法，建議密契都應該由挑戰關卡去獲取!", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
